title: VA  Ku De Ta 3 - Crafted by Donni 1 (2008) [ChillOut][mp3 192-32
description:
VA  Ku De Ta 3 - Sunset Soundtracks Crafted by Donni 1 
Year: 2008
Label: Level Two Music
Bitrate: 192-320 kbps

Since its inception in 2000 , KU DE TA in Seminyak , Bali has consistently pushed boundaries , taking the beach - front, bar restaurant , sunset experience to new standards and refining its iconic summertime tropical tempo which is punctuated by the now legendary high season party series.

Now in its 3rd year the KDT compilation series is a multi media package featuring a sublime sunset soundtrack , blending a 70 minute mix of balearic beats , soul and hi tech jazz , cuts from Kraak & Smaak , Ben Westbeach , Alkmx , and Jazzanova will provide the perfect soundtrack to your Summer.

The accompanying DVD is a 50 minute production that recreates the party series of 2007 backed by a soundtrack of evergreen house music with cuts from Joey Negro , Blue Six and the stone cold classic Gat Decor track "Passion" , the DVD illustrates the images from the island of life, beautifully shot and edited celebrating the nature and people of Bali and KU DE TA. ~ www.recordstore.co.uk

The third Global Release from Asia's seminal style setter.

"Ku De Ta 3 ,with all its colour and depth is the finest chill out set to come this way in 2008" Inpress (Album of the week) 

" The KDT compilation series is a multimedia distillation of this summertime odyssey" " Dj Donni 1 has fashioned a sublime sound track to summer" Out in Perth

" Unlikely to take a holiday in Bali soon, this could make up for it " 3 stars Herald Sun Hit Mag 

"Classy new package, fashion forward tunes and a desirable high season party DVD" MCV 

" Kick off the cocktail hour with Balearic Beats, soul and hi tech jazz" Grazia
